            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Please refer to the Tender Package for more details.</P>
               <P>The Heat Management Contract consists of the maintenance of 141 Housing sites of which 40 are Multi-storey blocks of flats that are part of district heating systems; 3 are cold water distribution pumped sites and 58 are site-based laundry plant rooms.</P>
               <P>The services covering weekly tests at all blocks, fan maintenance, twice yearly boiler servicing, tank cleaning, electrical testing, monitoring of underground mains and general painting cleaning of all sites.</P>
